<li><a href="/wiki/Robert_Sedgewick_(computer_scientist)" title="Robert Sedgewick (computer scientist)">Robert Sedgewick</a>: <i>Algorithms in C</i>, Addison-Wesley, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0201314525" class="internal">ISBN 0-201-31452-5</a> (Part 14) and <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0201316633" class="internal">ISBN 0-201-31663-3</a> (Part 5)</li>
<li>William H. Press, Saul A. Teukolsky, William T. Vetterling, Brian P. Flannery: <a href="/wiki/Numerical_Recipes" title="Numerical Recipes">Numerical Recipes</a> in C (The Art of Scientific Computing), <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0521431085" class="internal">ISBN 0-521-43108-5</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
